Class HybridPlot

    • edu.cross.ucsc.hse.core.chart.HybridPlot

  • public class HybridPlot
extends java.lang.Object
    A plot generated by a configuration that allows any additional changes to the subfigures using the JFreeChart APIs, or for use in any GUI applications.
